snippet.title: Compensation not Guaranteed - Wishlist Now on Steam!
snippet.description:
Welcome to Compensation Not Guaranteed, a new document-checking game from Team Project Lunch.

In this game, you will encounter a diverse cast of characters, each with their own stories and stakes, as you decide whether or not they deserve compensation for their land. Stay focused on meeting your quota and deadline, but don’t forget to keep an eye on public approval—every decision counts.

- - - - -

Wishlist the game on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2795590/Compensation_Not_Guaranteed/

- - - - -

Developer: Team Project Luch
Publisher: Toge Productions
